Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Luna, come sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It’s become quite clear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:51.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You’ve let your heart grow far too fond
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How can you say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don’t we deserve bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:02.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is it a crime~ to share a bond?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Can we never love, never just disobey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But he is a king, the same royalty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t matter, at least not to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even still
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You must know that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:27.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Heavy is the crown we wear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:32.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Why must it be, the burden I bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:40.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How can I live with a broken heart~~~?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:24.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well hello my dear, I thought you had gone~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:33.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes I did but now we~ need to~ talk~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I have been thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My heart’s been sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:46.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I don’t think we can go on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You must be playing…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:57.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What could have changed, what did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Please, you do not share the blame
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It’s already killing me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:10.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I’ll watch you grow old and gray
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:14.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But you will
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You must know that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:22.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Heavy is the crown we wear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:26.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Missing the short-lived life that we share
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:35.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Left to grieve for all eternity~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:40.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Heavy is the crown we wear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That is the cost, the burden I bear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:56.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sombra, please, you have to~ let me go~~~~